{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb69b6085-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"300ff–31b"},"text":"§ 300ff–31b.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Authorization of appropriations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb69b6086-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For the purpose of carrying out this subpart, there are authorized to be appropriated $1,195,500,000 for fiscal year 2007, $1,239,500,000 for fiscal year 2008, $1,285,200,000 for fiscal year 2009, $1,349,460,000 for fiscal year 2010, $1,416,933,000 for fiscal year 2011, $1,487,780,000 for fiscal year 2012, and $1,562,169,000 for fiscal year 2013. Amounts appropriated under the preceding sentence for a fiscal year are available for obligation by the Secretary until the end of the second succeeding fiscal year.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idb69b6087-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reservation of amounts","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb69b6088-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Emerging communities","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Of the amount appropriated under subsection (a) for a fiscal year, the Secretary shall reserve $5,000,000 for grants under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–30"},"text":"section 300ff–30 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idb69b6089-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Supplemental grants","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idb69b608a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b/b/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Of the amount appropriated under subsection (a) for a fiscal year in excess of the 2006 adjusted amount, the Secretary shall reserve ⅓ for grants under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–29a"},"text":"section 300ff–29a of this title","children":[],"tail":", except that the availability of the reserved funds for such grants is subject to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–28/a/2/H"},"text":"section 300ff–28(a)(2)(H) of this title","children":[],"tail":" as applied for such year, and except that any amount appropriated exclusively for carrying out "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–26"},"text":"section 300ff–26 of this title","children":[],"tail":" (and, accordingly, distributed under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–28/a/2/F"},"text":"section 300ff–28(a)(2)(F) of this title","children":[],"tail":") is not subject to this subparagraph."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idb69b608b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–31b/b/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" 2006 adjusted amount","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of subparagraph (A), the term “2006 adjusted amount” means the amount appropriated for fiscal year 2006 under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–77/b"},"text":"section 300ff–77(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":" (as such section was in effect for such fiscal year), excluding any amount appropriated for such year exclusively for carrying out "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–26"},"text":"section 300ff–26 of this title","children":[],"tail":" (and, accordingly, distributed under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s300ff–28/a/2/I"},"text":"section 300ff–28(a)(2)(I) of this title","children":[],"tail":", as so in effect)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb69b608c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1944-07-01/ch373"},"text":"July 1, 1944, ch. 373","children":[],"tail":", title XXVI, § 2623, as added and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/109/415/tII/s208"},"text":"Pub. L. 109–415, title II, § 208","children":[],"tail":", title VII, § 703, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2006-12-19"},"text":"Dec. 19, 2006","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/120/2801"},"text":"120 Stat. 2801","children":[],"tail":", 2820; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/87"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–87","children":[],"tail":", §§ 2(a)(1), (3)(A), (c), 5(c)(3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2009-10-30"},"text":"Oct. 30, 2009","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/123/2885"},"text":"123 